results.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
results.synopsis: From his pineapple home base under the sea, SpongeBob and his friends, including his meowing pet snail Gary, get into memorable misadventures.

results.title: Gotham
results.synopsis: Long before he was commissioner, rookie cop James Gordon takes on Gotham City crime and corruption to avenge the murder of Bruce Wayne's parents.

results.title: Popples
results.synopsis: The adorable Best Popple Pals love helping their friends and neighbors, but every time they do it seems to backfire in hilarious ways.

results.title: Versailles
results.synopsis: King Louis XIV of France commissions a lavish palace that becomes a fierce battleground for love and politics -- and a gilded prison for nobility.

results.title: A Certain Magical Index
results.synopsis: Supernaturally gifted teen Tōma teams up with nun Index against evil forces seeking powerful magical texts that have been implanted in Index's mind.

results.title: Future Diary
results.synopsis: A boy is forced into a survival game in which players equipped with diaries that can predict the future compete to become the god of space and time.

results.title: Street Fighter II: V
results.synopsis: Ryu and his friend Ken are martial arts fanatics who traverse the globe in search of new techniques to improve their skills in this anime series.

results.title: When They Cry
results.synopsis: New to rural Hinamizawa, Keiichi discovers a series of murders in its past. But his new friends refuse to speak of them and seem to be monitoring him.

results.title: Miraculous: Tales of Ladybug and Cat Noir
results.synopsis: When Paris is in peril, Marinette becomes Ladybug. Little does she know, her school crush Adrien is actually Cat Noir, another city-saving superhero.

results.title: A Certain Scientific Railgun
results.synopsis: Mikoto uses her ability to control electricity to help maintain order in Academy City, most of whose inhabitants are mystically gifted students.

results.title: Baby Ballroom
results.synopsis: Step into the cutthroat world of kids' ballroom dancing, where ambitious instructors, proud parents and pint-sized performers waltz to win.

results.title: Sleepless Society: Nyctophobia
results.synopsis: Following the death of her child, a grief-stricken woman struggles to find peace until a mysterious boy appears, claiming to be her reincarnated son.

results.title: Penalty
results.synopsis: At a Lucknow college, an aspiring football player’s dream of playing nationally is threatened when he faces discrimination for his Manipuri background.

results.title: No Guns Life
results.synopsis: An ex-soldier with a revolver for a head takes a hunted boy under his wing, putting himself in the crosshairs of the oppressive Berühren Corporation.

results.title: Finding Hubby
results.synopsis: Oyin and her two close friends are on the hunt for husbands, but find that they must grapple with their own expectations as they look for love.

results.title: The Tour
results.synopsis: Miloš Knor brings comedians Lukáš Pavlásek, Tomáš Matonoha, Ester Kočičková, Michal Kavalčík and Richard Nedvěd on a tour around the Czech Republic.

results.title: Saiyuki
results.synopsis: A renegade priest, a monkey king, a lecherous water sprite and a sympathetic demon team up to form an unlikely band of warriors.

results.title: Deep in the Rainforest
results.synopsis: Filmmakers Rainer Bergomaz and Yung Sandy travel through remote rainforests to observe the massive black caiman and the rare harpy eagle.

results.title: Dream Routes
results.synopsis: This documentary series explores stunning travel routes throughout Southern and Central Asia, with spotlights on diverse landscapes and cultures.

results.title: Wilder Iran
results.synopsis: In this documentary, nature photographer Benny Rebel embarks on a multiweek expedition to capture images of wildlife native to his homeland of Iran.

results.title: Wild Switzerland
results.synopsis: Discover the glistening lakes, breathtaking glaciers, ancient forests and unique plants and animals of the Swiss Alps in this nature series.

results.title: Wild Italy
results.synopsis: This two-part documentary shows off Italy's wild side, from pink flamingos and sure-footed ibex up north to wild horses and giant sharks in the south.

results.title: The Women Saving Our Seas
results.synopsis: A group of scientists and activists battle extreme temperatures and sleep deprivation while working for weeks on end to save the world's oceans.

results.title: The Silicon Valley Revolution: How a Few Nerds Changed the World
results.synopsis: Today, Silicon Valley is home to tech companies that are worth billions. But their beginnings were ad hoc, chaotic and revolutionary.

results.title: Battlefield Behemoths: A History of the Tank – The World Wars.
results.synopsis: Filmed just over a century after the first tank battle in 1918, this documentary series explores how the vehicles forever changed warfare.

results.title: Blue's Clues & You!
results.synopsis: Follow the paw prints of preschool pup Blue to solve playful puzzles, meet new friends and figure out her special messages with new pal Josh.

results.title: Encounters
results.synopsis: To please her mother, a woman sets out to find a husband, and makes an ambitious plan to find a match — and get married — within one year.

results.title: Una festa esagerata
results.synopsis: A Neapolitan family hosts an over-the-top party to climb the social ladder, but an unexpected event in their building threatens to thwart their plans.
